+-->
+
+Get the default value for `verbatim` in [`dns.lookup()`][] and
+[`dnsPromises.lookup()`][]. The value could be:
+
+* `ipv4first`: for `verbatim` defaulting to `false`.
+* `verbatim`: for `verbatim` defaulting to `true`.
